<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.4.9">
<l>peṟṟat talaivaṉeṅ kōmāṉ pēraru ḷāḷaṉ matalāy</l>
<l>cuṟṟak kuḻāttiḷaṅ kōvē tōṉṟiya tolpuka ḻāḷā</l>
<l>kaṟṟi ṉantōṟuma ṟittuk kāṉamti rinta kaḷiṟē</l>
<l>yeṟṟuk keṉammamuṇ ṇātē yemperumā ṉirun tāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Great leader, my king, the one of copious grace, oh child,</l>
<l>Young  king of [our] clan assembly, the one of ancient glory</l>
<l rend="indent">who appeared [incarnate],</l>
<l>Elephant who wanders the forest, guarding each calf herd,</l>
<l>For what [reason] have you stayed [away], my lord, not suckling my milk?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
